### 8. Termination

#### 8.1 Automatic Termination

Your rights under this license terminate automatically if you:
- Fail to comply with the attribution palimpsest requirement
- Remove or obscure previous authors' attributions
- Violate the copyleft requirement (relicense under permissive license)
- Initiate patent litigation (see Section 5)

#### 8.2 Reinstatement

If your rights terminate due to non-compliance:
1. Rights are automatically reinstated if you cure the violation within 30 days
2. Rights are permanently reinstated if the copyright holder explicitly reinstates them
3. Reinstatement does not affect any claims for damages from the violation

